o the House is a share, fasting is a share, enjoining good is a share, forbidding evil is a share, and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32265,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/18\/which-handle-islam-reliable\/","url_meta":{"origin":33178,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Love: Which handle of Islam is most reliable?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara\u2019 ibn \u2018Azib reported: We were sitting with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cWhich handle of Islam is the most firm?\u201d They said, \u201cPrayer.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIt is good, but that is not it.\u201d They said, \u201cCharity.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIt is good,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6563,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/best-jihad-women-hajj-umrah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33178,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Best jihad for women is Hajj pilgrimage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, shall we not attend the military expeditions and fight in jihad alongside you?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo, rather the best and most beautiful jihad for you is the Hajj, a blessed pilgrimage.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323